{"tid":239981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【崇光感謝慶】逾百中國客烈日排隊 搶購限量化妝品","createTime":"2017-05-12T05:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T05:30:59.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f21009ee1a18d70e6bc8994a14f35c9d3646328f","tid":239981,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T05:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170512/large/1494564404_a691.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170512%2Flarge%2F1494564404_a691.jpg&h=ecf8452e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n半年一度崇光百貨（SOGO）感謝周年慶今日開鑼，首輪周年慶今日起一連10日舉行，SOGO早上10時始營業，惟以過往人潮逼滿軒尼詩道行人路三角位相比，今年的人潮未站滿半個三角位。<br />\n<br />\n今次感謝慶以限購化妝品套裝最受歡迎，早上9時多已有百多人排隊，當中以內地遊客為主，更有男士撐住拐杖排隊。以往大受女士歡迎的花花煲「Le Creuset」，首日感謝慶推出100個Lavender心形鑄鐵鍋，折售$2,388，惟相比過去長長人龍，今次乏人問津，僅10多人排隊。<br />\n<br />\n上午11時許，店外仍有數百人，在烈日當空下排隊，購買化妝品牌Estee Lauder的限購套裝，成為SOGO最受歡迎優惠產品。除了化妝品區，SOGO內各層未見人頭湧湧，其中在花花煲「Le Creuset」店內，職員更比顧客多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56683640&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56683640%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170512&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUiv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=9af52ae9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56683640%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170512&h=9007929c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56683640&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170512</a>"},{"pid":"f8f608684f204be1e5d2b1fbd254ac6cba8df6b6","tid":239981,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T05:30:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}